quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  6,9,neez agar hum kisi farishta ko bhaijtay to usay mard ki soorat mein bhaijtay aur jo shuba ( ab ) karte hain isi shay mein phir inhen daal dete
  6,10,aur tum se pehlay bhi payghambaroon ke sath tamaskhur hotay rahay hain so jo log un mein se tamaskhurkiya karte they un ko tamaskhur ki saza ne aa ghera ا
  6,11,kaho ke ( ae munkareen risalat ) malik mein chalo phiro phir dekho ke jhutlanay walon kakiya injaam howa
  6,12,( un se ) pucho ke aasman aur zameen mein jo kuch hai kis ka hai keh do khuda ka is ne apni zaat ( pak ) par rehmat ko lazim kar liya hai woh tum sab ko qayamat ke din jis mein kuch bhi shak nahi zaroor jama kere ga jin logon ne apne aap ko nuqsaan mein daal rakha hai woh imaan nahi laatay
  6,13,aur jo makhlooq raat aur din mein bastii hai sab isi ki hai aur woh santa jaanta hai
  6,14,kahokiya mein khuda ko chore kar kisi aur ko madadgaar bunun ke ( wohi to ) asmano aur zameen ka peda karne wala hai aur wohi ( sab ko ) khana deta hai aur khud kisi se khana nahi laita ( yeh bhi ) keh do ke mujhe yeh hukum howa hai ke mein sab se pehlay islam laane wala hon aur yeh ke tum ( ae paighambar! ) mushrikon mein nah hona
  6,15,( yeh bhi ) keh do ke agar mein apne perwar-digaar ki nafarmani karoon to mujhe barray din ke azaab ka khauf hai
  6,16,jis shakhs se is roz azaab taall diya gaya is par khuda ne ( barri ) meharbani farmai aur yeh khuli kamyabi hai
  6,17,aur agar khuda tum ko koi sakhti pohnchaye to is ke siwa is ko koi daur karne wala nahi aur agar Nemat ( o rahat ) ataa kere to ( koi is ko roknay wala nahi ) woh har cheez par Qadir hai
  6,18,aur woh apne bundon par ghalib hai aur woh Dana aur khabardaar hai
